          </p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_52ws' title='Col. 52WS &mdash; HC Deb 28 February 2003 vol 400 c52WS' name='column_52ws' href='#column_52ws' rel='bookmark'>52WS</a><p>&#x00A3;35.751 million as a result of re-classifying meat hygiene service (MHS) costs from administration to programme and refining the FSA's and MHS's budget for 2002&#x2013;03.</p>
